Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,保佑我能得奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,泉学长要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,棒球看来是玩不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事 继续玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可是对手球队没来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,红白战 红白战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\1a&H3C&\bord0\fs22\frz5.059\pos(819.2,269.8)}虽然下雪了 来玩业余棒球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,瑛太没有回复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,连已读都没有显示 可能是在睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可能像往常一样 默默地在背后做着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙有时候就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fad(50,0)\bord0\fs20\pos(323.2,612)}虽然下雪了 来玩业余棒球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fad(50,0)\fn@FZShaoEr-M11\bord1\fs22\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(551.2,548)\frz258.6}刚看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fad(50,0)\fnFZShaoEr-M11\bord1\fs20\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(280.533,488)}不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fad(50,0)\bord0\fs24\pos(330,417)}没事的话  你也来玩吧
